                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.9331/70: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-07-26T09:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 26, 1928—9 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>240. Your 569, July 25, 6 p.m. Unless it is too late, suggest publication of
                    treaty be held up for a few days or until about August 1st as you previously
                    suggested. Please cable immediately.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
